st og p\u00e5 disse er det veldig liten vits i \u00e5 pr\u00f8ve isfiske n\u00e5. I Blomstertj\u00f8nna finnes det imidlertid fortsatt liv.", "- Her skal det v\u00e6re en del stor \u00f8rret. Selv om vi ikke fikk sett noen i dag, regner jeg med at minst \u00e9n av dem havner p\u00e5 en krok i neste uke, smiler Simavik.", "LES OGS\u00c5: Her settes \u00f8rreten tilbake i Ilavassdraget", "PS. Fiskekort i Blomstertj\u00f8nna koster 60 kroner per d\u00f8gn og kan kj\u00f8pes via SMS. Personer under 16 \u00e5r fisker gratis.", "F\u00f8lg Adresseavisen p\u00e5 Facebook , Instagram og Twitter ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6b044a746a4da06745322853bc5a2e4d9e86b623b379306d306065d51b67f9da"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-19T17:42:55.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Neste uke blir det full isfiskeservice p\u00e5 Blomstertj\u00f8nna i Bymarka."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article14239815.ece/97ydj/ALTERNATES/w980-default/doc6tp6jb65kpl176red3fb.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/18773bbf707ccd5ba5a625cb5db2972ef3414f6c.jpg?598f0f79"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Tilbyr gratis fiskestang, agn og ferdigborede hull -adressa.no", "Trygg is", "Muligheter for stor \u00f8rret"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "18773bbf707ccd5ba5a625cb5db2972ef3414f6c"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Vinterferie", "Bymarka", "fiske"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Vinterferie,Bymarka,fiske"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "sports"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["isen", "trenger", "fiske", "ferdigborede hull", "agn", "hull", "gratis"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "v